{"tid":1758304,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE多腎又柒出國際 隊友同主持都忍唔住笑","createTime":"2019-11-27T03:20:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T15:46:27.000Z","uid":222155,"like":6,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"97ba07a19daede787e0f1e4df49676df7bb06b01","tid":1758304,"uid":222155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:20:56.000Z","msg":"2019 Asia Artist Award 昨日(26/11)於越南舉行，當主持人問到TWICE的服裝設計時，隊長大山婆馬上把咪高峰傳到「綠茶婊子」多腎手上，因為估計到她會扮可愛講啲濕膠答案。<br />\n<br />\n多腎果然不負眾望，解釋佢哋今日嘅黑白配搭概念係&ldquo;kookeu&rdquo; (忌廉與曲奇)。話口未完， 已經引來全場捧腹大笑，包括主持人和隊友。<br />\n<br />\nONCE (TWICE粉絲團) 發言人表示，對多腎今次的言論表示遺憾，並予以最強烈譴責，促請多腎注意言行，不要再讓團隊增添麻煩。<br />\n<br />\n(譯：葡葡適)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.koreaboo.com/news/twice-nayeon-2019-asia-artist-awards-laughing/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreaboo.com%2Fnews%2Ftwice-nayeon-2019-asia-artist-awards-laughing%2F&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRJugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=9ca46e4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.koreaboo.com/news/twice-nayeon-2019-asia-artist-awards-laughing/</a>"},{"pid":"0a1a6efc7d75e09a5ae2d71c7a22001a7d41d49a","tid":1758304,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:21:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QWeEy2B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQWeEy2B.png&h=90138a27&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fgsiPAW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfgsiPAW.png&h=78ef3435&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n怕香港人善忘嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n想聲援理大手足嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n和理非嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n勇武嘅，推行動 post 啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係行動post，星期三晚，我地聚首商場，以和理非聲援理大手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756593\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fbebddddfb69f8b7870a88dc9a10177d03094454","tid":1758304,"uid":74065,"like":18,"dislike":10,"score":8,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:22:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lh3.google